{"title":"读雪","authors":["杨国显"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":2,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"读雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨国显"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透过新年的钟声我看见"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"博大而恢宏的音流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开光芒万丈的白色巨翅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天地间悠悠翔飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦古老而又年轻的日历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿越时空隧道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照耀唐诗宋词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彪炳着华夏文明呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷扬扬了千万年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"静静地落下来无声无息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伸手托起一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝眸看时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面是历史的结束"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面是纪元的开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在西域以西"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽见皎娇处女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楚楚动人地裸露着原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜甜睡姿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美丽得令人颤栗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰盈的躯体向天际铺展"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰清玉洁的肌肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映入眼帘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁离去的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串脚印"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"省略了赞美的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪橇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握住冰天雪地轻轻扬鞭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犬吠鹿鸣或者马嘶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都可以响亮地拉起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的向往执著地前行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有了长长的诗歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫过古朴的民风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一次次照亮我们的视野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"令人诵读辞旧迎新的含义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这么沿着崭新的走向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"匆匆地赶路间或大喝一声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天离我们越来越近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寒冬离我们越来越远"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}